biography:
Claire Keim (born Claire Lefebvre 8 July 1975) is a French actress and singer.

Keim was born in Senlis, Oise to an architect and a dentist. She is in a relationship with French footballer Bixente Lizarazu, and lives in Saint Jean de Luz and Paris. She gave birth to their daughter Uhaina in August 2008.
